</a></strong></div>
					<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
				<div style="clear: left;">
															<p>Yes there are certainly some great books out there for kids with special needs and they typically address that feeling of being different.  Books are typically geared to a particular diagnosis.  Does he have aspergers?  There seem to be quite a few books for aspergers kids that have been published recently- even fiction (main character has aspergers and solves mysteries).  These books typically address the social issues and what kids can do about them.  I know less about LD books- but have seen them in major bookstores...</p>
																				</div>
